At first glance, it seems difficult to be optimistic.
Although the ceasefire agreed on November 21st is still in place, this week's fighting has strengthened the forces on both sides.
Leaders of Hamas, the Islamist movement that has ruled Gaza since 2007, will boast of forcing Israelis to give up, even though Gaza has been beaten.
